Text: RE confidentiality agreementMark Thanks I will work on getting this executed ASAP Talk to you soon Nick Original Message From McConnell Mark mailto Sent Tuesday November AM To Subject confidentiality agreement Nick Attached is the confidentiality agreement Please print out a couple of copies sign and return Upon receipt and our signatures well pass forward all the information we have to help you create the weather product we discussed last month Call me if you have any questions Mark Aquila confident doc Mark McConnell Transwestern Pipeline Company office cell fax This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you

RE CONFIDENTIALITY AGREEMENTMark I have two executed originals headed your way via US Mail I will also fax you a signed copy to expedite matters Once you all have executed forward one original back to Shelby Walnut Suite Kansas City MO Thanks and I look forward to working with you Nick Original Message From McConnell Mark mailto Sent Monday November AM To Leibhart Shelby Thomas Nicholas Subject RE CONFIDENTIALITY AGREEMENT Shelby All of your changes are fine and have been accepted by our legal group Attached is the latest version with your suggestions added Please execute two copies and send back them to me Thanks for your help with this matter Mark phone fax Transwestern Pipeline Company Smith Street Houston Texas Original Message From Leibhart Shelby mailto Sent Wednesday November AM To McConnell Mark Subject CONFIDENTIALITY AGREEMENT Mark Attached is the CA you sent to Nick Thomas He forwarded it to me for review and I have included our proposed changes in the attachment redlined If acceptable please revise and send back an executable version to me and to Nick If you have any questions or would like to discuss please contact me Aquila confident doc Thanks Shelby Leibhart Contract Analyst Aquila Inc phone fax This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you
